The paper discusses the design of compact deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Specifically, the paper focuses on algorithms that automatically search for compact network architectures, which is a subfield of deep learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
